            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間20日11:44，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲12.11點（或3.25%），暫報384.45點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+6.54%</li><li>近 1 月：+12.9%</li><li>近 3 月：+26.17%</li><li>近 6 月：+42.51%</li><li>今年以來：+34.79%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電概念股概念領漲+6.54%。其中    家登(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3680:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3680\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3680-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        帆宣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6196:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6196\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6196-TW</a>)            上漲        9.89%            ;        創意(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)            上漲        9.83%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>18吋晶圓概念領漲+6.20%。其中    盟立(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2464:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2464\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2464-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        家登(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3680:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"http